---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Astradic | Screen time blocking app"
  description="Astradic is a screen time blocking app that locks distracting apps and sites, enforces limits, and protects your focus."
>
  <header class="nav">
    <a class="logo" href="/">
      <span class="brand-name">Astradic</span>
    </a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#pillars">Pillars</a>
      <a href="#how">How it works</a>
      <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" style="color: #fff;" href="https://forms.fillout.com/t/bW7CakbWKCus">Get early access</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div>
        <span class="pill">Screen time blocking, redesigned</span>
        <h1 class="fade-in delayed">Block distractions. Reclaim your focus.</h1>
        <p class="lede fade-in more-delayed" style="margin-top: 10px;">
          Astradic locks distracting apps and sites, enforces limits, and keeps your attention where it matters.
        </p>
        <div class="cta-row fade-in more-delayed">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" style="color: #fff;" href="https://forms.fillout.com/t/bW7CakbWKCus">Get early access</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="mailto:contact@astradic.org">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-card fade-in more-delayed">
        <div class="hero-grid">
          <div class="cell">
            <span class="tiny">Block lists</span>
            <strong>Apps + sites</strong>
            <p>Lock the biggest time sinks the moment you start a focus session.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cell">
            <span class="tiny">Schedules</span>
            <strong>Automatic focus</strong>
            <p>Set recurring windows that protect your deep work every day.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cell">
            <span class="tiny">Limits</span>
            <strong>Hard boundaries</strong>
            <p>Stop doomscrolling with firm caps and intentional unlocks.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cell">
            <span class="tiny">Insights</span>
            <strong>Focus signals</strong>
            <p>Review your patterns and tighten what drains your attention.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="pillars">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div>
          <span class="pill">Why Astradic</span>
          <h2>Screen time control without constant willpower</h2>
          <p>
            Astradic combines distraction blocking, focus rituals, and smart limits so you can do your best
            work without fighting your phone every hour.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag">Distraction shield</span>
          <h3 class="feature-title">App and website blocking</h3>
          <p>Build focus lists for social, news, or entertainment apps and lock them with one tap.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag">Focus routines</span>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Schedules that stick</h3>
          <p>Automate recurring focus windows so your best hours stay protected.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag">Accountability</span>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Limits with intention</h3>
          <p>Use hard caps, cooldowns, and friction to make breaks deliberate instead of automatic.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="how">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div>
          <span class="pill">How it works</span>
          <h2>Plan, protect, review</h2>
          <p>Set up your focus plan once, then let Astradic enforce it in the moments that matter.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="feature-title">1. Map your distractions</h3>
          <p>Choose the apps, sites, or categories that pull you off task and add them to a block list.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="feature-title">2. Design focus windows</h3>
          <p>Create deep-work sessions, commute modes, or evening wind-downs that repeat automatically.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="feature-title">3. Learn and refine</h3>
          <p>Review focus trends, tighten limits, and keep your schedule aligned to your goals.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="use-cases">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div>
          <span class="pill">Built for real life</span>
          <h2>Who Astradic helps</h2>
          <p>
            Whether you are trying to reclaim deep work or cut late-night scrolling, Astradic gives you a
            clear, consistent system.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="feature-title">Deep work pros</h3>
          <p>Block distracting apps during creative or technical work so you can stay in flow longer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="feature-title">Students and learners</h3>
          <p>Keep study time distraction-free with scheduled focus sessions and smart limits.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="feature-title">Families and parents</h3>
          <p>Create healthier routines with consistent limits and shared focus windows.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="faq">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div>
          <span class="pill">FAQ</span>
          <h2>Common questions</h2>
          <p>Everything you need to know before joining the early access list.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="feature-title">Is Astradic available now?</h3>
          <p>Astradic is in active development. Join the early access list to be the first to try it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="feature-title">What can Astradic block?</h3>
          <p>Build custom block lists for distracting apps, websites, and habits you want to limit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="feature-title">Will it work with my schedule?</h3>
          <p>Yes. You can set recurring focus windows, quick sessions, or time-based limits that fit your day.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
    {JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "FAQPage",
      mainEntity: [
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          name: "Is Astradic available now?",
          acceptedAnswer: {
            "@type": "Answer",
            text: "Astradic is in active development. Join the early access list to be the first to try it.",
          },
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          name: "What can Astradic block?",
          acceptedAnswer: {
            "@type": "Answer",
            text: "Astradic lets you create custom block lists for distracting apps, websites, and habits you want to limit.",
          },
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          name: "Will it work with my schedule?",
          acceptedAnswer: {
            "@type": "Answer",
            text: "Yes. You can set recurring focus windows, quick sessions, or time-based limits that fit your day.",
          },
        },
      ],
    })}
  </script>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;">
        <strong class="brand-name">Astradic</strong>
        <span style="color:var(--muted);">Screen time blocking</span>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
        <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/astradic_org">@astradic_org</a>
        <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} Astradic. All rights reserved.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
